Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### [2.1.9] Quý trong tương lai
GET http://localhost:9999/api/transactions/journal?range=FUTURE
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### [2.1.10] Năm nay
GET http://localhost:9999/api/transactions/journal?range=THIS_YEAR
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### [2.1.11] Năm ngoái
GET http://localhost:9999/api/transactions/journal?range=LAST_YEAR
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### [2.1.12] Năm trong tương lai
GET http://localhost:9999/api/transactions/journal?range=FUTURE
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### [2.1.13] Tùy chỉnh - Quý 1/2026 (Frontend lấy startDate/endDate từ UtilController rồi gọi CUSTOM)
GET http://localhost:9999/api/transactions/journal?range=CUSTOM&startDate=2026-01-01T00:00:00&endDate=2026-03-31T23:59:59
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### [2.1.14] Tùy chỉnh - Quý 2/2026
GET http://localhost:9999/api/transactions/journal?range=CUSTOM&startDate=2026-04-01T00:00:00&endDate=2026-06-30T23:59:59
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### [2.1.15] Tất cả thời gian (Chế độ "Xem tất cả" trên UI)
GET http://localhost:9999/api/transactions/journal?range=CUSTOM&startDate=2000-01-01T00:00:00&endDate=2099-12-31T23:59:59
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### [2.1.16] Lỗi: Thiếu range lẫn startDate/endDate
# Kỳ vọng: 400 Bad Request - "API yêu cầu phải có 'range' hoặc cả startDate và endDate"
GET http://localhost:9999/api/transactions/journal
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

